        <changelogtext>[font color=black]In written numbers, you can now click on cells to jump around during memory and recall.[/font]</changelogtext>
        <changelogtext>[font color=black]The score panel now expands about half way up the screen instead of all the way.[/font]</changelogtext>
    </changelogversion>

